# --- 私人工作內容：只追蹤框架骨架與說明，忽略實際論文與個人素材 ---

# 實際編修的論文（每篇一夾）為私人內容；只保留範本骨架與說明
papers/*
!papers/_TEMPLATE/
!papers/README.md

# 風格素材為私人內容（含蒸餾摘要）；只保留 README 與 sources 佔位檔
# 個人筆法
writing-style/personal-voice/*
!writing-style/personal-voice/README.md
!writing-style/personal-voice/sources/
writing-style/personal-voice/sources/*
!writing-style/personal-voice/sources/.gitkeep
# 學術英文原則
writing-style/academic-principles/*
!writing-style/academic-principles/README.md
!writing-style/academic-principles/sources/
writing-style/academic-principles/sources/*
!writing-style/academic-principles/sources/.gitkeep